% parrot0 lexical knowledge - curated closed-class/function words.
% Loaded as base knowledge by brain_create before the optional world/session
% layers, so filters can consult the KB without persisting these facts.
% Predicates exported: stopword/1, conjunction/1.

% gen193 (KB-migration direction, PRINCIPLES.md): coordinating conjunctions are
% KNOWLEDGE, not a hardcoded C word array. List parsers query conjunction/1 to
% split a coordinated phrase, so the class can GROW at runtime: teaching parrot0
% "use p as a conjunction" asserts conjunction(p) and the very same parsers then
% split on "p" with no code change. The engine is fixed; the lexicon learns.
conjunction(and).
conjunction(or).
conjunction(e).
conjunction(ed).
conjunction(o).
conjunction(oppure).

